# Store Pattern

## HOOK-ENFORCED (will be blocked)

Every feature with state MUST use this store directory structure:

```
features/{feature-name}/store/
├── atoms.ts       # Base and derived atoms
├── families.ts    # atomFamily definitions (if needed)
├── actions.ts     # Write atoms (mutations)
├── listeners.ts   # Side-effect hooks
├── handlers.ts    # Message handlers
└── types.ts       # Store-specific interfaces
```

Files outside this pattern in a store directory will be blocked.

## Naming Conventions (HOOK-ENFORCED)

| File | Export Pattern | Example |
|------|---------------|---------|
| atoms.ts | `*Atom` | `projectsAtom`, `activeThreadAtom` |
| families.ts | `*AtomFamily` | `threadAtomFamily`, `tabsAtomFamily` |
| actions.ts | `do*Atom` | `doSwitchThreadAtom`, `doAddTabAtom` |
| listeners.ts | `use*Listeners` | `useThreadStoreListeners` |
| handlers.ts | `create*Handlers` | `createThreadHandlers` |

Exports that don't match these patterns will be blocked.
